                     <interp inst="t18530131-232-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>. Aged 22.—<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy on account of his previous character.</hi>
                  </rs>—
